@baseUrl = http://localhost:18160

### 리뷰 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "productId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "orderId": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
  "rating": 5,
  "content": "리뷰 내용",
  "imageUrls": "https://example.com/review1.jpg,https://example.com/review2.jpg"
}

### 리뷰 수정
@reviewId = 44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/reviews/{{reviewId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "content": "수정된 리뷰 내용",
  "imageUrls": "https://example.com/review1-updated.jpg"
}

### 리뷰 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/reviews/{{reviewId}}

### 특정 상품 리뷰 목록 조회
@productId = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222

GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/reviews?productId={{productId}}

### 내가 작성한 리뷰 목록 조회
@userId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/reviews?userId={{userId}}